about.LicenseAgreement: Nekushandisa iyi software, unobvumirana nemitengo yeNeuralium software rezenisi chibvumirano. Unogona kutarisa yazvino vhezheni yesoftware chibvumirano pane:

account.PleaseImportOrCreateWalletAccount: Ndokumbira utore kana kugadzira wallet account

verifyAccount.Title: Kuzivisa Akaundi
verifyAccount.IntroductionText: Kuti udzivirire kushungurudzwa, iyo yekugadzira account account inofanirwa kupfuura neimwe nzira yekutarisirwa. Zvichienderana nekuti iwe uripi, sarudzo dzakasiyana dziripo.
verifyAccount.ResultsSuccess: Kwazvo kwakabudirira! yako account ID iri zvino kusimbiswa nefoni.
verifyAccount.ResultsFailure: Verification yaive yekutadza. Unogona kuedza zvakare mumaawa makumi maviri nemana.
verifyAccount.DefaultHelpText: Pano iwe unofanirwa kusarudza nzira yekuongorora pakati pezvisarudzo zviripo. Imwe neimwe nzira ine zvayakanakira uye zvisingafadzi. Ndokumbira utore iyo yakakunakira iwe.
verifyAccount.TESTNETHelpText: MuTESTNET, kuongororwa kunogona kupfuurwa kuti ugadzire account izvozvi.
verifyAccount.AppointmentsHelpText: Iwe unozotanga iyo Neuralium kugadzwa yekumisikidza maitiro. Maitiro aya anogona kutora mazuva mazhinji uye uchafanirwa kuve uripo pakugadzwa kwako kana zuva racho rasimbiswa. Betsero: isingazivikanwe.
verifyAccount.POWHelpText: Iwe uchafanirwa kuitisa nguva inodhura CPU chiratidzo chebasa. Kana ichinge yapera, account yako inozogona yangu mune 1 uye 2nd tiers seSeva.

appointments.Title: Kugadzwa Verification
appointments.IntroductionText: Kugadzika kwekufambiswa kwakagadzirirwa kusimbisa vashandisi vakagadzirirwa nguva ichichengeta iyo yakawanda yemafashama kunze kwehurongwa.
appointments.RequestAppointmentText: Kuti utange kuita izvi, ndokumbirawo ubvunze musangano zvakanyanya. Chikumbiro chekugadziriswa chichaitwa uye chisimbiso chinofanirwa kugamuchirwa munguva inotevera.
appointments.AppointmentRequestedText: Wako kugadzwa kwanyorwazve. Tinofanira kumirira iko kusimbiswa.
appointments.AppointmentConfirmedText: Chikumbiro chako chekusarudza chakasimbiswa uye zuva uye nguva yatarwa zvino. Ita shuwa yekupinda munguva!
appointments.AppointmentVerificationRequestedText: Chikumbiro chekutarisirwa kuiswa chakatumirwa. Isu takamirira iko kusimbiswa.
appointments.InvalidPuzzleEngineVersion: Isingashandiswe pipi injini vhezheni. Ndokumbira kuti uwedzerezve shanduro yako yesoftware.

puzzles.Title: Mifananidzo
puzzles.TimeBeforeAppointment: Yako yepuzzle chikamu chinozotanga munguva pfupi. Inofungidzirwa nguva yasara pamberi pekukumbira kugadzwa kwako
puzzles.WaitingForPuzzle: chikamu chepuzzle chinofanira kutanga chero nguva ikozvino. Parizvino yakamirira mirairo yepuzzle ...
puzzles.CompletedAndSend: Mapipi ako apedzwa. Ndokumbira umire apo mhinduro dzirikuitwa.
puzzles.PreparingPackage: Ndokumbira umire apo chirongwa chekugadzwa chinopedzisa uye chinotumira mhedzisiro yekusimbisa.

accountPublication.AccountPublicationProcessExplanation: Pamberi pese mabasa anogona kuitwa pane blockchain, yako account inofanira kuiswa pachena kune vamwe. Akaunti yako ichasimbiswa, uye ichave yakagadzirira kushanda kana ichinge yasimbiswa mubhuroko.
accountPublication.AccountPublicationFailed: Pane chikanganiso chakaitika panguva yekuburitsa iyo account. Veruzhinji vakatadza.
accountPublication.CanCloseWindow: Iwe unogona ikozvino kuvhara iyi windo zvakachengeteka iwe uchimirira iyo simbiso kuti isvike.
accountPublication.NeedBlockchainSynced: Blockchain inoda kuwiriraniswa kuitira kuti ibudise account.
accountPublication.NeedPeerToPublish: Hazvina kukwana peer chakabatana kuitira kuti utange kuburitsa account.

mining.ExplainInfoPanel: Akasiyana anobatsira infomation adn nhamba nezve ako emigodhi zvikamu
mining.Explain: Pano unogona kuisa komputa yako kuti iite nekuita kuti iite masvomhu mapuzzle kuvhura maNeuraliums matsva.
mining.Miningportalert: Ongorora: Kuti uite mine, yako TCP pachiteshi inofanira kuwiriraniswa nedzimwe nzvimbo dziri p2p. Kugovera ndiko hunhu hwakakodzera pane p2p. Kana uchishuwira mine mine mune yechipiri neyekutanga emigodhi mamati, chiteshi CHINOGONA kuve chakabatana kana zvisiri izvo node yacho haizombobudirira mine mine block. Ndokumbira uve nechokwadi chekuvhura firewall yako uye kugonesa kutumira port.
mining.ConfirmClearCachedCredentials: Zvinofanirwa here kuti zvinyorwa zvemugodhi zvicherwe? (izvi zvinogona kukanganisa kuita zvisina kunaka uye hazvikurudzirwe)
mining.PortNotConnectableCantMine: Kuti ugove wangu mune 1st kana 2nd tiers, yako p2p port inofanirwa kuve inogona kuunganika. Haikwanise kugonesa migodhi sezvazviri. Kana iwe usingakwanise kuvhura chiteshi, saka gadzira minerals kuti ishande mune yechitatu.

testMode.ParagrahOne: Iwe parizvino uri muTESTNET modhi. Iyo testnet vhezheni inorehwa kuti uyedze nehuhu hutsva izvo zvingave kana zvingasaita sekufunga. Iwe unogona kutaurira chero bugs, matambudziko kana mazano aungave nawo pane edu akazvipira mhinduro.
testMode.ParagrahTwo: Mune TESTNET modhi, chero mitsipa yemagetsi inowanikwa ndeyekuongororwa chinangwa chete uye inogona kusashandiswa mukugadzira 'MainNet' network. Tokens yakawanikwa muTESTNET modhi inogona zvakare kurasika kana kugadzirisa zvakare chero panguva pasina ziviso yekutanga.
testMode.Warning: Iyo node uye chikwama chiri ikozvino muTestNet Mode kune imwe network.
testMode.Period: Iyi TESTNET kuvaka inoshanda kusvika Nyamavhuvhu 18th 2020.

wallet.PleaseCreateOrCopy: Gadzira chikwama chitsva kana kurodha chiripo.
wallet.WalletWaitMessage: Tave kuumba yako account uye chengetedzo kiyi. Izvi zvinogona kutora akawanda maminitsi. Ndatenda nekutsungirira kwako.
wallet.Completed: Chikwama chako chakagadzirwa zvakanaka. Zvino sedanho rinotevera, isu tinokurudzira kuti uite backup yekuchengetedza yako wallet yese folda. Isu tinokurudzirawo kuti ubvise kiyi yepamoyo kubva kuaccount yako uye uichengete zvakachengeteka pane imwe drive kunze kwekomputa yako.
wallet.WalletPath: Iwe unogona kutsvaga chikwama chako chitsva munzira inotevera
